Tamatlah riwayat kita.

647
01:27:42,630 --> 01:27:43,673
Kau hendak ke mana?

648
01:27:43,756 --> 01:27:44,966
Mengumpulkan teman-teman.

649
01:28:04,443 --> 01:28:06,153
Bersiap berlabuh!

